All Implemented Interfaces:
java.awt.event.WindowListener, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, java.util.EventListener, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, URLs
public class JWSApplet
extends javax.swing.JApplet
implements java.awt.event.WindowListener, URLs

this is an entrypoint for Java Web Start when it thinks it is launching an applet. In this case, appletcontext exists that will supply values for getCodeBase and getDocumentBase this can also be used in the mode where lots of parameters are supplied so no web server is needed. The decision is made based on "serverkey" parameter, for which a dummy value bypasses contacting the real server.
